2023 Year of the RABBIT Chinese New Year Card

Review 2023 Year of the RABBIT Chinese New Year Card – Chinese New Year Cards Popular 2023 Year of the RABBIT Chinese New Year Card help you save during this period 2023 Year of the RABBIT Chinese New Year Card See more about itModern, minimalist HAPPY CHINESE NEW YEAR flat greeting card to celebrate THE YEAR OF THE RABBIT in 2023. The design shows the symbol of the RABBIT in the Chinese Zodiac. ‘Year of the Rabbit’ and ‘2023’ appear either side of the symbol. 2023 is CUSTOMIZABLE, so you can update when required for subsequent RABBIT years. At the bottom, there is a Christian Bible verse based on 3 John 2 – MAY YOU PROSPER AND BE IN HEALTH, EVEN AS YOUR SOUL PROSPERS, which relates to the Chinese blessing of prosperity. Customize the greeting on the back by personalizing the text with your own message. Variations of this design are available in the CHINESE NEW YEAR Collection by Berean Designs, where you can choose from a wide selection of cards, gifts, clothing and home decor. This card is also available in red. Price:$2.11
